OL,5,G1005 Trucking Hell
OL,6,     FThe men and women working in the
OL,7,     Fheavy recovery business are
OL,8,     Ffollowed, as they tackle
OL,9,     Fjack-knifed lorries, crashed heavy
OL,10,     Fgoods vehicles and roadside
OL,11,     Fbreakdowns.
OL,12,G1105 Outback Truckers
OL,13,     FSteve and dog Bella are in a race
OL,14,     Facross the red deserts of
OL,15,     FAustralia hauling classic cars to
OL,16,     Fauction but delays in loading and
OL,17,     Fthe arrival of the wet season
OL,18,     Fthreaten the journey home.
