OL,6,     FIn Suffolk, a series of farm
OL,7,     Fthefts wreak havoc until CCTV
OL,8,     Fprovides the vital clues police
OL,9,     Fneed to crack the case. Plus
OL,10,     Fshocking footage of the killing of
OL,11,     Fprotected wildlife.
OL,12,G0000 999: Criminals Caught on Camera
OL,13,     FDrug smugglers, boozed-up brawls
OL,14,     Fon the sea front and beach raves
OL,15,     Fthat get out of hand, plus
OL,16,     Fthieving seagulls and ice cream
OL,17,     Fwars - all Caught on Camera.
